            <description><![CDATA[<div id="page-content" class="rich_media_area_primary" style="">      <div class="rich_media_area_primary_inner">                                                        <div id="img-content" class="rich_media_wrp">                    <h1 class="rich_media_title " id="activity-name">            拜登儿子与俄音乐厅恐袭有关？          </h1>          <div id="meta_content" class="rich_media_meta_list">                                      <span id="copyright_logo" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta icon_appmsg_tag appmsg_title_tag weui-wa-hotarea">原创</span>                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">                                      老猫                                  </span>                                                              <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_nickname" id="profileBt">              <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight weui-wa-hotarea" id="js_name">                潘汝刚              </a>              <div id="js_profile_qrcode" aria-hidden="true" class="profile_container" style="display:none;">                <div class="profile_inner">                  <strong class="profile_nickname">潘汝刚</strong>                  <img class="profile_avatar" id="js_profile_qrcode_img" src="" alt="">                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">微信号</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">gh_7ba9b194226f</span>                  </p>                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">功能介绍</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">文章，图片，音乐。</span>                  </p>                </div>                <span class="profile_arrow_wrp" id="js_profile_arrow_wrp">                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_out"></i>                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_in"></i>                </span>              </div>            </span>            <span id="meta_content_hide_info">              <em id="publish_time" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text"></em>              <em id="js_ip_wording_wrp" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text" role="option" aria-labelledby="js_a11y_op_ip_wording js_ip_wording" style="display: none;"><span id="js_a11y_op_ip_wording" aria-hidden="true"></span><span aria-hidden="true" id="js_ip_wording"></span></em>                          </span>          </div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  <div class="rich_media_content js_underline_content                       autoTypeSetting24psection            " id="js_content" style="visibility: hidden;"><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100006975" data-ratio="1.7770833333333333" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0UO7rlYQibavPleshF0pBnqLHj7knVdoevqibAUic7lu4vyHGR9iapCbuR4W19XjntXZekmhk7jVqhMQVbyucOBU9g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="480" style=""></p><p>乌克兰说是伊斯兰国恐怖组织干的，</p><p>美国说与此事无关，<br></p><p>伊斯兰国也承认是自己干的。</p><p>这似乎形成了三角铁证，<br></p><p>就是伊斯兰国干的。<br></p><p>但是克格勃出身的普京就是不相信，<br></p><p>伊斯兰国凭啥平白无故的干这件事？<br></p><p>幕后一定有操控者。<br></p><p>果不然调查有了新的结果。<br></p><p>拜登儿子涉嫌恐袭？</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100006978" data-ratio="0.5857142857142857" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0UO7rlYQibauIh45ho3c1rtWXJflDKGzSc72XuA7Rle5rxgjvYGMgtymkewhlvqguRN49OUiaf68PHiaZElWCPOTw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="700" style=""></p><p cms-style="font-L"><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 17px;font-weight: 800 !important;">俄罗斯调查委员会目前正围绕“检查数百万美元的收入来源和进一步的资金流动”进行调查，重点检查“西方国家政府官员、民间和商业组织人员中的特定个人”是否参与其中；</span></strong></span></p><p cms-style="font-L"><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 17px;font-weight: 800 !important;">最关键的一点，那就是俄调查委员会认定，乌克兰的一些商业团体，尤其是石油和天然气公司布利斯马控股公司，提供资金用于近年来在俄罗斯发动恐怖袭击；</span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: left;">布利斯马控股公司是乌克兰最大的天然气公司，拜登家族和这家公司有着很深的利益瓜葛，<span style="color: rgb(255, 41, 65);">拜登之子亨特·拜登</span>曾于2014-2019年在这家公司担任董事，并且有消息人士称，这家公司向拜登父子每人支付了500万美元的贿赂！</p><p style="text-align: left;">以上消息，这几天在网上传的沸沸扬扬。</p><p style="text-align: left;">依照老猫这种资历、阅历以及所处的阶层，<br></p><p style="text-align: left;">不可能知道详细的内幕。<br></p><p style="text-align: left;">毕竟克格勃与中情局都没搞通。</p><p style="text-align: left;">只是试图从逆向逻辑推理，提出个人观点，以飨读者。<br></p><p style="text-align: left;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px;">首先弄明白什么是伊斯兰国：</span></strong><br></p><p style='margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;text-align: start;'><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">伊斯兰国，全称为“伊拉克和大叙利亚伊斯兰国”，简称ISIS，是一个极端的恐怖主义组织。它的出现和发展，与中东地区的复杂历史、政治、宗教等多种因素密切相关。</span></p><p style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;text-align: start;'><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">伊斯兰国的前身可以追溯到2004年，当时一个名为“基地组织在伊拉克”的组织在伊拉克境内活动。</span></p><p style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;text-align: start;'><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">2013年，该组织更名为“伊拉克和大叙利亚伊斯兰国”，并在同年4月宣布建立“伊斯兰国”。</span></p><p style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;text-align: start;'><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">伊斯兰国的主张是建立一个严格遵守伊斯兰教教法的国家，其行为包括对异教徒和不同意见的穆斯林进行暴力攻击，对文化遗产进行破坏，以及对平民进行大规模的迫害和屠杀。这些行为引起了国际社会的广泛谴责。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100006979" data-ratio="0.5654545454545454" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/0UO7rlYQibauIh45ho3c1rtWXJflDKGzSQchiaC1LZzmtKDtw8ziaZ9fyqYZAY3Rtib1DzeeQUJic1KHF8VepDdYQMQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="550" style=""></p><p style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;text-align: start;'><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">提起伊斯兰国就不能不说起原教旨主义。</span></p><p style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;text-align: start;'><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">首先，让我们来了解一下什么是原教旨主义。</span></p><p style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;text-align: start;'><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">原教旨主义通常指的是一种宗教观念，强调对宗教教义的严格、字面的解释和遵守。</span></p><p style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;text-align: start;'><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">在伊斯兰教中，原教旨主义特指严格遵守古兰经和圣训的教导，拒绝现代解释或其他宗教创新。</span></p><p style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;text-align: start;'><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">原教旨主义的信徒可能属于不同的派别，有的温和，有的可能极端。</span></p><p style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;text-align: start;'><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">而伊斯兰国（Islamic State of Iraq and Syria，简称ISIS）是一个曾经在中东地区活动的极端主义组织。</span></p><p style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;text-align: start;'><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">该组织以其极端的宗教理念和激进的行为而闻名，包括对异教徒和不同意见的穆斯林进行暴力攻击，对文化遗产进行破坏，以及对平民进行大规模的迫害和屠杀。</span></p><p style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;text-align: start;'><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);">伊斯兰国在其控制区域内试图实施一种极端的原教旨主义形式</span><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">的伊斯兰教法。</span></p><p style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;text-align: start;'><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">如果上述这些有点深奥，<br></span></p><p style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;text-align: start;'><strong><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 18px;">老猫不妨举个简单的实例：</span></strong></p><p style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;text-align: start;'><span style='font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;text-align: justify;'>伊朗的头巾规定源于伊斯兰教义，该规定要求女性在公共场合戴上头巾，以遮盖头发和颈部。</span><br></p><p style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;text-align: start;'><span style='font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;text-align: justify;'>头巾规定的由来可以追溯到伊斯兰教的原始文本——《古兰经》和《圣训》中的教义。伊斯兰教认为，女性是宝贵的财产，应该得到尊重和保护。在伊斯兰教传统文化中，女性被视为家庭和社区的重要组成部分，需要在公共场合表现出谦虚、谨慎和保守的形象。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100006980" data-ratio="1.6375" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0UO7rlYQibauIh45ho3c1rtWXJflDKGzSUazQL56J7CQ7licFSm5KEliacnELcUVmu971IiaM5uGVm5xlicqNLkFovw/640?wx_fmt=webp&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="webp" data-w="640" style=""></p><p style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;text-align: start;'><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">其实这就是原教旨主义的一种表现。</span></p><p style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;text-align: start;'><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">阿富汗塔利班政府禁止女性读大学，就更是一种原教旨主义了。</span></p><p style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";text-align: start;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: arial;letter-spacing: 2px;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">阿富汗临时政府高等教育部长表示该决定是在阿富汗内阁会议上做出的，阿富汗临时政府高等教育部发言人证实称，高等教育部向阿富汗的私立与公立大学发送信函，要求大学根据内阁决定立即暂停招收女性学生，并在正式实施禁令后通知教育部。</span></p><p style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";text-align: start;'><span style="font-size: 17px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: arial;letter-spacing: 2px;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">这项禁令颁布于阿富汗女性参加完高中毕业考试的几周后。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100006981" data-ratio="0.6578125" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0UO7rlYQibauIh45ho3c1rtWXJflDKGzSBxjlDXINCY6z3hsq763mbuGa6iaDsMKvshbwj4mesZQpHlhCGQpCvuQ/640?wx_fmt=webp&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="webp" data-w="640" style=""></p><p style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";text-align: start;'><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: arial;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">曾经在课堂里接受教育的阿富汗女性。</span><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;"><br></span></p><p style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";text-align: start;'><span style="font-family: arial;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);">值得指出的是，</span></p><p style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";text-align: start;'><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: arial;text-align: start;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;background-color: rgb(255, 251, 0);">原教旨主义的最大敌人就是耶稣教</span><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: arial;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">。<br></span></p><p style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";text-align: start;'><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: arial;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">这两大宗教过去水火不相容。</span></p><p style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";text-align: start;'><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: arial;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">其中就有世界史上著名的十字军东征。<br></span></p><p style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";text-align: start;'><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: arial;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><br></span></p><p style='margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;text-align: start;'><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">十字军东征是一系列<span style="font-size: 17px;font-weight: bolder;">发生在1096年至1291年间的宗教性军事行动</span>。</span></p><p style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;text-align: start;'><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><br></span></p><p style="white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: transparent;line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 17px;font-weight: bolder;">背景与原因</span>：</span></p><p style="white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: transparent;line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;"><span style='letter-spacing: 2px;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";text-align: start;font-weight: bolder;'>1】宗教动机</span><span style='letter-spacing: 2px;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";text-align: start;'>：</span><span style='letter-spacing: 2px;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";text-align: start;'>基督教和伊斯兰教之间长期存在着圣地争夺，尤其是耶路撒冷对基督徒具有特别的宗教意义。</span></p><p style="white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: transparent;line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;"><span style='letter-spacing: 2px;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";text-align: start;'>2】</span><span style='letter-spacing: 2px;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";text-align: start;font-weight: bolder;'>政治因素</span><span style='letter-spacing: 2px;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";text-align: start;'>：</span><span style='letter-spacing: 2px;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";text-align: start;'>西欧的一些封建领主寻求通过军事征服来扩大领土和影响力。</span></p><p style="white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: transparent;line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;"><span style='letter-spacing: 2px;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";text-align: start;'></span><span style='letter-spacing: 2px;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";text-align: start;font-weight: bolder;'>3】经济因素</span><span style='letter-spacing: 2px;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";text-align: start;'>：</span><span style='letter-spacing: 2px;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";text-align: start;'>当时的欧洲社会经历了人口增长和经济压力，一些无地骑士和贫穷贵族希望通过征战获得财富。</span></p><p style="white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: transparent;line-height: 26px;word-break: break-word;"><span style='letter-spacing: 2px;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";text-align: start;'></span><span style='letter-spacing: 2px;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";text-align: start;font-weight: bolder;'>4】教皇支持</span><span style='letter-spacing: 2px;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";text-align: start;'>：</span><span style='letter-spacing: 2px;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);color: rgb(7, 19, 62);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";text-align: start;'>罗马天主教会希望通过军事行动推进基督教的扩张，并增强教权的地位。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 17px;font-weight: bolder;">5】著名的领导者</span>：包括英格兰的狮心王理查、法国的路易七世等都参与了这些东征。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100006982" data-ratio="0.6963350785340314" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0UO7rlYQibauIh45ho3c1rtWXJflDKGzSUoZygYEiawYvNMISJcMTeyoaznwlMKosJJ1QAicC6iaVlicJibOH38qAolg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="382" style=""></p><p><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;">应该说事情发展到现在，</span><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;"></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">以美国为首的西方基督教势力，与阿拉伯国家为代表的伊斯兰教势力仍然充满着矛盾。<br></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">毋庸置疑</span></strong><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">，阿拉伯世界、基地组织、伊斯兰国的最大共同敌人就是美国。</span></p><p><strong><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 20px;">那么问题就来了</span></strong><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">，<br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">伊斯兰国为啥放着最大的敌人不去恐袭，反而袭击与美国作对的俄罗斯？<br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">相比之下，美国更容易被袭击，尤其是中东的那些军事基地。<br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">相反，俄罗斯更不好惹，更加戒备森严。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">孰重孰轻？<br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">伊斯兰国为啥舍近求远呢？<br></span></p><p><strong><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 18px;">更加巧合的是</span></strong><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">，<br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">恐袭事件恰恰发生在俄乌战争的关键时刻。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">这难道还不值得发人深省吗。<br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">如果说俄罗斯情报部门提供的仅仅是孤证，<br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">那么原教旨主义者与美国的水火不相容状况，就是旁证了。</span></p><p><strong><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 18px;">还有一件事更值得推敲</span></strong><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">，<br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">那就是俄罗斯揭露拜登儿子的丑闻，有利于将来特朗普胜选。<br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;background-color: rgb(255, 251, 0);">普京做梦都想着特朗普当选呢</span><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;">。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100006983" data-ratio="0.541" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0UO7rlYQibauIh45ho3c1rtWXJflDKGzSuDgOvxJfDibGxkEK3bdkpsia7Edibzuyms1blrFTRiaJAicZB3IHK302HPw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1000" style=""></p><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p></div>          <script type="text/javascript" nonce="1897651257" reportloaderror>            var first_sceen__time = (+new Date());            if ("" == 1 && document.getElementById('js_content')) {              document.getElementById('js_content').addEventListener("selectstart",function(e){ e.preventDefault(); });            }          </script>        </div>                        <div id="js_tags_preview_toast" class="article-tag__error-tips" style="display: none;">预览时标签不可点</div>                        <div id="content_bottom_area" class="rich_media_tool_area"></div>                              </div>    </div>]]></description>
